com.tomtom.speedtools.services.lbs.geocode

Interface GeoCodeEngine

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TomTomLbsGeoCodeEngine

    public interface GeoCodeEngine
    This interface wraps the TomTom LBS Geocoding functionality, found at http://lbs.tomtom.com.

    • Method Summary

    • Method Detail

      • query

        @Nonnull
GeoCodeEngineResponse query(@Nonnull
                                     String query)
                              throws AuthorizationException,
                                     ServiceUnavailableException,
                                     IOException
        Basic query (without additional parameters). No input validation is performed on input query.
        Parameters:
        query - Free-text query to execute (according to LBS specification). May be empty.
        Returns:
        Response. In case of an error, count == 0.
        Throws:
        AuthorizationException - Thrown if API key is rejected by server.
        ServiceUnavailableException - Thrown if the service is (temporarily) unavailable.
        IOException - Thrown if query to geo coder fails for some other reason.

      • query

        @Nonnull
GeoCodeEngineResponse query(@Nonnull
                                     String query,
                                     @Nonnull
                                     String parameters)
                              throws AuthorizationException,
                                     ServiceUnavailableException,
                                     IOException
        Query with additional parameters. No input validation is performed.
        Parameters:
        query - Free-text query to execute (according to LBS specification). May be empty.
        parameters - Parameter set (see UrlParameterBuilder). If null or empty, this method equals the query method without parameters.
        Returns:
        Response. In case of an error, count == 0.
        Throws:
        AuthorizationException - Thrown if API key is rejected by server.
        ServiceUnavailableException - Thrown if the service is (temporarily) unavailable.
        IOException - Thrown if query to geo coder fails for some other reason.

      • query

        @Nonnull
GeoCodeEngineResponse query(@Nonnull
                                     String query,
                                     @Nonnull
                                     GeoRectangle boundingBox)
                              throws AuthorizationException,
                                     ServiceUnavailableException,
                                     IOException
        Query with bounding box (convenience function). Internally calls .UrlParameterBuilder to add bounding box as a query parameter. No input validation is performed.
        Parameters:
        query - Free-text query to execute (according to LBS specification). May be empty.
        boundingBox - Valid bounding box.
        Returns:
        Response. In case of an error, count == 0.
        Throws:
        AuthorizationException - Thrown if API key is rejected by server.
        ServiceUnavailableException - Thrown if the service is (temporarily) unavailable.
        IOException - Thrown if query to geo coder fails for some other reason.

      • query

        @Nonnull
GeoCodeEngineResponse query(@Nonnull
                                     String query,
                                     @Nonnull
                                     GeoRectangle boundingBox,
                                     @Nullable
                                     String parameters)
                              throws AuthorizationException,
                                     ServiceUnavailableException,
                                     IOException
        Query with bounding box and parameters (convenience function). Internally calls .urls.ParameterBuilder to add bounding box as a query parameter. No input validation is performed.
        Parameters:
        query - Free-text query to execute (according to LBS specification). May not be null, but may be empty.
        boundingBox - Valid bounding box (other than wrong API key).
        parameters - Parameter set (see UrlParameterBuilder). If null or empty, this method equals the query method without parameters.
        Returns:
        Response. In case of an error, count == 0.
        Throws:
        AuthorizationException - Thrown if API key is rejected by server.
        ServiceUnavailableException - Thrown if the service is (temporarily) unavailable.
        IOException - Thrown if query to geo coder fails for some other reason.
